footage shows that the person impersonating

00:05:12.190 --> 00:05:13.310
Hu Bo for a withdrawal

00:05:13.310 --> 00:05:14.920
is the same one

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:17.240
arguing with Liu Wanyao.

00:05:18.430 --> 00:05:19.270
That's him.

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:22.950
This guy's called Ding Chuan.

