00:08:38.720 --> 00:08:39.870
on Hu Bo's bones.

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:57.360
If something's up, just say.

00:08:57.510 --> 00:08:58.960
I don't want anyone else to see me.

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:02.870
I'm here to give something back.

