(Zhao Xiaozhe)

00:09:07.790 --> 00:09:09.150
- You...
- Your son is fine.

00:09:10.390 --> 00:09:11.630
I mean, he's fine now.

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:12.960
Whether he'll always

00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:14.360
be fine is uncertain.

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:15.240
You're crazy!

00:09:20.870 --> 00:09:21.710
Hello?

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:22.920
Yes, honey.

00:09:23.080 --> 00:09:24.510
Is Xiaozhe okay?

00:09:24.510 --> 00:09:25.350
Is he with you?

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:26.440
He...

00:09:28.270 --> 00:09:29.200
What are you doing?

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:30.390
Why not let her hear?

00:09:32.150 --> 00:09:33.320
Then let's show her.

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:36.200
At your son's

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:37.720
kindergarten performance,

00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:39.960
everyone will point at

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:41.320
you and your wife.

00:09:43.390 --> 00:09:45.150
Your son will seriously ask,

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:47.750
"Dad, who's that lady?"

00:09:48.150 --> 00:09:50.030
- "What are you doing?"
- Stop it.

00:09:50.030 --> 00:09:51.510
At your company's team-building event,

00:09:51.510 --> 00:09:52.790
this video will also be shown.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:55.030
All your colleagues

00:09:55.750 --> 00:09:57.080
will quietly be gossiping,

00:09:57.870 --> 00:09:58.910
"Didn't expect

00:09:59.840 --> 00:10:02.550
Mr. Zhao to be like this."

00:10:02.550 --> 00:10:04.320
Stop it. Stop it.

00:10:04.630 --> 00:10:05.510
You want money, right?

00:10:05.670 --> 00:10:06.600
Just tell me how much.

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:07.440
I don't want money.

00:10:09.670 --> 00:10:11.080
Someone wants me to tell you

00:10:11.720 --> 00:10:13.080
that the truth is out there.

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:15.390
It will eventually be found.

00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:33.440
Are you sure

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:34.840
these marks were originally there?

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.870
We first thought it was a coincidence.

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:38.240
But on the victim's

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:39.720
other arm and leg bones,

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:40.750
there were no matching nails,

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:42.390
only on this side,

00:10:42.390 --> 00:10:43.270
in a regular pattern.

00:10:43.670 --> 00:10:44.630
We only noticed something

00:10:44.630 --> 00:10:46.030
strange when we photographed

00:10:46.030 --> 00:10:47.030
the bones yesterday.

00:10:52.630 --> 00:10:53.960
Check Morse code.

00:10:58.030 --> 00:10:58.870
Hello?

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:00.030
Hello? Are you Officer Xu?

00:11:00.030 --> 00:11:00.870
Yes.

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:02.440
- You asked me call you
- Check this out.

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:03.480
when Mr. Zhao's back.

00:11:03.870 --> 00:11:05.390
He'll have a meeting this afternoon.

00:11:05.390 --> 00:11:06.240
He just called

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:07.080
and told us to prepare.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:08.080
Okay.

00:11:08.080 --> 00:11:09.790
So I come now?

00:11:09.980 --> 00:11:10.840
Yes.

00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:11.750
Captain He,

00:11:11.750 --> 00:11:12.720
Zhao Xueli is back.

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:13.560
I should go.

00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:15.480
Bring Liu Ming with you.

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:16.920
Okay.

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:25.550
Does the police suspect Mr. Zhao?

00:11:25.790 --> 00:11:27.030
He must be involved in this.

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:28.670
It's hard to explain.

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:29.910
I don't know.

00:11:29.910 --> 00:11:31.080
Finance Unit took projects?

00:11:31.630 --> 00:11:33.030
There must be something fishy.

00:11:33.030 --> 00:11:34.900
(Jinrun Investment Group)

00:11:41.270 --> 00:11:42.750
That's destroying evidence.

00:11:43.670 --> 00:11:45.360
I didn't expect Mr. Hu would be like this.

00:11:52.840 --> 00:11:53.790
Hello,

00:11:53.790 --> 00:11:54.660
I'm Liu Ming,

00:11:54.660 --> 00:11:56.140
(Police)
CIU 1 Officer.

00:11:56.790 --> 00:11:57.630
This is my colleague.

00:11:58.910 --> 00:12:00.200
- Hi, Mr. Zhao.
- Hi, Officer.

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:03.240
Your hands are so sweaty.

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:04.910
Remember to stay hydrated

00:12:04.910 --> 00:12:05.960
and get enough rest.

00:12:06.120 --> 00:12:07.390
Are you overworked

00:12:07.390 --> 00:12:08.480
without Hu Bo,

00:12:08.910 --> 00:12:10.240
your capable right-hand?

00:12:11.870 --> 00:12:12.870
He hadn't worked for days.

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:14.790
My colleagues and I were very worried.

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:15.870
What an incident.

00:12:16.150 --> 00:12:17.000
That's a reason to worry.

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:19.270
Please sit down.

00:12:19.270 --> 00:12:20.800
- Mr. Zhao, please.
- You too.

00:12:21.030 --> 00:12:21.910
Who did he go with?

00:12:22.390 --> 00:12:23.230
Liu Ming.

00:12:24.270 --> 00:12:25.240
Alright, I got it.

00:12:25.240 --> 00:12:26.080
Okay.

00:12:31.960 --> 00:12:33.440
Please ask whatever you want.

00:12:33.440 --> 00:12:34.380
I'll answer everything I know.

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:37.790
We'd like to ask you something

00:12:37.790 --> 00:12:38.630
about Hu Bo.

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:42.960
Well, Hu Bo...

00:12:43.220 --> 00:12:44.740
(Unknown)

00:12:44.840 --> 00:12:46.240
Please wait. I need to take this call.

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:47.080
Okay.

00:12:58.270 --> 00:12:59.110
Officer Liu,

00:12:59.670 --> 00:13:00.750
I've got a lead.

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:02.320
It's about Hu Bo.

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:04.750
I want to tell you in detail.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:11.270
How many years has your company been around?

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:12.200
Thirteen years.

00:13:12.200 --> 00:13:13.040
No,

00:13:13.550 --> 00:13:14.390
twelve years.

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:17.320
Quite a long time.

00:13:18.630 --> 00:13:19.600
What have you been doing

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:20.840
for twelve years?

00:13:21.240 --> 00:13:22.910
We do financial consulting.

00:13:23.750 --> 00:13:25.790
What did Hu Bo do in the company?

00:13:26.550 --> 00:13:27.390
He only handled

00:13:27.910 --> 00:13:29.480
our internal financial management.

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:30.320
He was introverted.

00:13:42.200 --> 00:13:43.630
(If you want to stay safe,)

00:13:43.790 --> 00:13:45.120
(tell me the mastermind)

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:45.960
(behind you.)

00:13:46.270 --> 00:13:47.110
(Otherwise,)

00:13:47.390 --> 00:13:49.480
(your wife and son will die.)

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:01.840
Double-layer encryption.

00:14:02.120 --> 00:14:03.080
We need the key

00:14:03.080 --> 00:14:04.320
to unlock the final message.

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:05.840
Let me try.

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:11.550
(The police found you.)

00:14:11.910 --> 00:14:13.510
(Keep your mouth shut.)

00:14:13.510 --> 00:14:14.720
(I'll be there in a minute.)

00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:15.560
(You're coming with me.)

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:23.800
Was Hu Bo

00:14:24.200 --> 00:14:26.270
on good terms with his wife?

00:14:26.750 --> 00:14:27.870
My wife is a terrible cook.

00:14:28.200 --> 00:14:29.320
I promised my son

00:14:29.320 --> 00:14:31.270
I'd take him out for burgers.

00:14:31.480 --> 00:14:33.200
If I bail on him again,

00:14:33.200 --> 00:14:34.440
he'll definitely be mad.

00:14:34.440 --> 00:14:35.320
Don't get me wrong.

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:38.200
My son is actually really cute.

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:39.040
Really cute.

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:43.320
You know, Officer Xu,

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:45.960
I'm not feeling well today.

00:14:46.240 --> 00:14:48.030
If you don't have other questions...

00:14:48.030 --> 00:14:48.910
But I do.

00:14:52.930 --> 00:14:53.790
I didn't know

00:14:53.790 --> 00:14:56.000
you weren't feeling well today, Mr. Zhao.

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:58.600
I'll give you my number.

00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:00.440
- Let's stay in touch...
- I'll get them.

00:15:02.510 --> 00:15:03.550
Paper and pen.

00:15:05.630 --> 00:15:06.480
Got them right here.

00:15:18.840 --> 00:15:19.960
Thank you, Mr. Zhao.

00:15:20.440 --> 00:15:21.750
The truth will be found.

00:15:22.440 --> 00:15:23.280
See you around.

00:15:23.870 --> 00:15:24.710
See you.

00:15:29.910 --> 00:15:30.750
Take care.

00:15:57.120 --> 00:15:57.960
Mr. Xu?

00:15:59.360 --> 00:16:00.200
This is the first time

00:16:00.200 --> 00:16:01.270
you've called me on your own.

00:16:02.390 --> 00:16:03.720
Does your overseas company

00:16:03.720 --> 00:16:05.080
have the technology to erase

00:16:05.080 --> 00:16:05.920
human biological data?

00:16:06.280 --> 00:16:07.120
Why are you suddenly

00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:08.120
interested in that?

00:16:10.200 --> 00:16:11.390
That's classified.

00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:12.440
I can't disclose it.

00:16:14.030 --> 00:16:14.870
So you do have it.

00:16:17.550 --> 00:16:18.390
Mr. Xu,

00:16:18.600 --> 00:16:20.120
no wonder you and Lu Ran were like brothers.

00:16:20.550 --> 00:16:22.030
He asked me the same thing.

00:16:22.910 --> 00:16:23.750
But

00:16:24.550 --> 00:16:25.480
why do you think

00:16:25.480 --> 00:16:26.320
Lu Ran asked?

00:16:26.750 --> 00:16:28.030
I'd like to know that too.

00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:31.200
He once said

00:16:32.510 --> 00:16:34.200
he hated where he came from.

00:16:35.550 --> 00:16:37.440
He felt like he was a monster

00:16:38.600 --> 00:16:40.600
who shouldn't have existed in this world.

00:16:41.390 --> 00:16:42.270
So,

00:16:43.120 --> 00:16:44.910
even the brother he admired most

00:16:45.840 --> 00:16:47.480
didn't want him around.

00:16:49.840 --> 00:16:50.840
He wanted to know

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:52.960
whether, without the DNA

00:16:53.720 --> 00:16:54.840
of Lu Youliang,

00:16:54.840 --> 00:16:56.470
that rapist, inside him,

00:16:57.600 --> 00:16:58.600
could he have lived

00:16:59.630 --> 00:17:01.360
a different life?

00:17:04.480 --> 00:17:05.640
Lu Ran is dead.

00:17:06.440 --> 00:17:07.510
What are you trying to say?

00:17:08.790 --> 00:17:11.000
Lu Ran fought desperately to change his fate,

00:17:12.750 --> 00:17:14.550
hoping the world would accept him.

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:17.200
I think he was

00:17:17.200 --> 00:17:18.040
too naïve.

00:17:19.920 --> 00:17:20.830
He didn't need approval

00:17:20.830 --> 00:17:22.110
from the whole world,

00:17:23.110 --> 00:17:24.200
only from the people

00:17:24.200 --> 00:17:25.350
he cared about.

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:27.830
I've heard you have extraordinary empathy.

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:28.840
So, I think

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:30.680
you must understand him,

00:17:31.350 --> 00:17:32.190
right?

